row.InputSentence1: Michael likes to go to the beach but has trouble swimming.
row.InputSentence2: During a beach trip his friends made a dare to him.
row.InputSentence3: They told him to go into deep water and he did.
row.InputSentence4: Michael got tired when he was out and started to yell for help.
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz1: He swam even farther out then his friends dared him too.
row.RandomFifthSentenceQuiz2: His friends helped him back to the shore.
